    "Supplementary Fig. 10 and Supplementary Table 18 show the benchmark results; Fig.",
    "5e and Supplementary Fig. 11 show examples of cancer-specific germline SVs; and Supplementary Fig.",
    "12 show examples from the benchmark.",
    "Here we present an updated version of the highly popular SV caller Sniffles (Fig. 1).",
    "Sniffles2 is a substantial improvement in terms of accuracy and runtime compared to all other commonly used long-read-based SV callers (Fig. 2)."
